Package org.apache.iceberg.expressions

Class AggregateEvaluator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.iceberg.expressions.AggregateEvaluator
  • public class AggregateEvaluator
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for evaluating aggregates. It evaluates each of the aggregates and updates the aggregated value. The final aggregated result can be returned by result().
